author: Play On Tabletop
description:
Welcome to Game 3 of out  Studio League Season 2!

Six players will play over the next 5 months to crown one winner!  We keep track of Wins and losses which populate an ever changing leaderboard leading to a single elimination tournament at the end. Lets see which player comes out on top!

One twist this season is that while a player is allowed to play any faction they want, they can never play the same detachment twice!  Time to test your skill no matter what.  Lets see who wins the fabled crown of Chadocles!

===============GAME INFO=============
Nick got inspired by the winning list at LVO 2025 and decided to give it a whirl while Tak is dusting off a favourite of his, the White Scars!  Fast bikes vs hordes of infantry let's go!

===============ARMY LIST=============
Space Marines
White Scars
Strike Force (2000 points)
Stormlance Task Force
Chaplain on Bike
Chaplain on Bike
Kor’sarro Khan
Lieutenant with Combi-weapon
Heavy Intercessor Squad
Drop Pod
Assault Intercessors with Jump P
title: Studio League Season 2 - Game 3 - White Scars vs Astra Militarum
